text:
Pleases be advised that when fedex drivers don't want or feel like delivering to a certain address, they put bad address in their system.I had a package being delivered to my grand child, a Easter dresss, I sent the package in plenty of time to get there before Easter but because it's out of the drivers way he continued to put bad address in the system.
I called fedex all day and was told it would be delivered but that wasn't the case, now my grand child has to go without her dress because this *** didnt feel like going that way.Unacceptable!!!!
Review about: Ground Delivering.
I liked: Customer service, Fed ex is fine except the drivers in my area.
I didn't like: Non-delivery of shipment.
